No. 705. No. 706. Webster Coal and Coke Company, Petitioner, v. A. J. Cassatt et al; and Pennsylvania Coal and Coke Company, Petitioner, v. A. J. Cassatt et al. April 29, 1907. Mr. John W. Griggs and Mr. George S. Graham for petitioners. Mr. John G. Johnson for respondents.

Petitions for writs of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit granted.'
